    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E92 M3, powered by the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This engine features individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio, providing an instantaneous throttle response and a soaring 8,400 RPM redline. The power is managed via a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox and sent to the rear wheels through an M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring maximum longitudinal and lateral acceleration. The chassis dynamics are preserved with aluminum-intensive suspension components and a carbon-fiber reinforced plastic (CFRP) roof for a lower center of gravity. This example has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including an inspection of the VANOS system and rod bearing clearance, ensuring the valvetrain and bottom end remain within factory tolerances. A purist's machine that balances high-performance engineering with road-going durability.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
